{"heading": "HIGH-RESOLUTION SIDESCAN FUNCTION", "text": "The EA has a side scan function that is ideal for object detection, the morphology of the sea bed, dredging control, and obstacle and wreck detection.

Objects in the side-scan view can be marked by a mouse click and the position information will be stored. This data can then be exported real-time to external software if connected to a GNSS positioning and heading device. The KONGSBERG Sonar Mosaic software is available for this purpose.

With an extra zoom function, interesting targets or objects can be scaled up for detailed inspection. The zoom area is freely adjustable, and the window can be positioned as an overlay on any part of the side-scan echogram"}

